import React, {useState} from 'react';
import { BrowserRouter as Router, Switch, Route, Link } from 'react-router-dom';
import List from '@material-ui/core/List';
import ListItem from '@material-ui/core/ListItem';
import ListItemText from '@material-ui/core/ListItemText';
import RasberryPi from "./RasberryPi";

export default function Navibar() {
  let [data, dataSet] = useState([
    {categori: 'Home', path: '/', component: ''},
    {categori: 'Rasberry Pi', path: '/rasberry-pi', component: 'RasberryPi'},
    {categori: 'Python', path: '/python', component: 'RasberryPi'},
    {categori: 'PHP', path: '/php', component: 'RasberryPi'},
    {categori: 'Java', path: '/java', component: 'RasberryPi'},
    {categori: 'Linux', path: '/linux', component: 'RasberryPi'},
    {categori: 'JavaScript', path: '/java-script', component: 'RasberryPi'},
    {categori: '아키바 정보', path: '/akihabara', component: 'RasberryPi'},
    {categori: 'micro:bit', path: '/micro-bit', component: 'RasberryPi'},
    {categori: '챗봇(ChatBot)', path: '/chat-bot', component: 'RasberryPi'}
  ]);

  return (
    <Router>
      <List>
        <ListItem button key='Home' component={Link} to='/'>
          <ListItemText primary='Home' />
        </ListItem>
        <ListItem button key='Rasberry Pi' component={Link} to='/rasberry-pi'>
          <ListItemText primary='Rasberry Pi' />
        </ListItem>
        <ListItem button key='Python' component={Link} to='/python'>
          <ListItemText primary='Python' />
        </ListItem>
        <ListItem button key='PHP' component={Link} to='/php'>
          <ListItemText primary='PHP' />
        </ListItem>
        <ListItem button key='Java' component={Link} to='/java'>
          <ListItemText primary='Java' />
        </ListItem>
        <ListItem button key='Linux' component={Link} to='/linux'>
          <ListItemText primary='Linux' />
        </ListItem>
        <ListItem button key='JavaScript' component={Link} to='/java-script'>
          <ListItemText primary='JavaScript' />
        </ListItem>
        <ListItem button key='아키바 정보' component={Link} to='/akihabara'>
          <ListItemText primary='아키바 정보' />
        </ListItem>
        <ListItem button key='micro:bit' component={Link} to='/micro-bit'>
          <ListItemText primary='micro:bit' />
        </ListItem>
        <ListItem button key='챗봇(ChatBot)' component={Link} to='/chat-bot'>
          <ListItemText primary='챗봇(ChatBot)' />
        </ListItem>
      </List>
      <Switch>
          <Route path='/rasberry-pi' component={RasberryPi}></Route>
          <Route path='/python' component={RasberryPi}></Route>
          <Route path='/php' component={RasberryPi}></Route>
          <Route path='/java' component={RasberryPi}></Route>
          <Route path='/linux' component={RasberryPi}></Route>
          <Route path='/java-script' component={RasberryPi}></Route>
          <Route path='/akihabara' component={RasberryPi}></Route>
          <Route path='/micro-bit' component={RasberryPi}></Route>
          <Route path='/chat-bot' component={RasberryPi}></Route>
      </Switch>
    </Router>
  );
}
